Wow, seriously.

78
00:06:27,130 --> 00:06:29,410
What the heck?

79
00:06:29,410 --> 00:06:32,490
- Who was it? 
 - Cha Joo Ik.

80
00:06:33,950 --> 00:06:37,960
How can he not change a bit?

81
00:06:38,960 --> 00:06:41,400
He must still think I'm his subordinate.

82
00:06:41,400 --> 00:06:43,990
He's just rude. Rude.

83
00:06:43,990 --> 00:06:47,020
He just wants me to come without any explanations.

84
00:06:50,560 --> 00:06:52,650
He wants me to come to his house.

85
00:06:52,650 --> 00:06:55,150
